name: Sharpsign O

sections.text:
#Orational reads rational in octal (radix 8).  For example,
      #o37/15 == 31/13
      #o777 == 511
      #o105 == 69 ;105_8
The consequences are undefined if the token immediately following the #O
does not have the syntax of an octal (i.e., radix 8) rational.
